{"word":"G4328 - προσδοκάω - prosdokáō - pros-dok-ah'-o - Expect","slug":"G4328","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσδοκάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prosdokáō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros-dok-ah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Expect"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03B4;&#x03BF;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - prosdokao&#x0304;</b> - <i>pros-dok-ah'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <b>&#x03B4;&#x03BF;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>dokeuo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>watch</i>); to <i>anticipate</i> (in thought, hope or fear); by implication to <i>await:</i> - (be in) expect (-ation), look (for), when looked, tarry, wait for."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4329\">G4329</a>"}]}